    {
      "id": "46AuG81NM4bD34bWAImLM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5913.8235632458845,
      "y": -49.17066000000011,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "1Y0k5oecvePAmEBAC5POE",
        "zPLCsPolUMNc7XS6cCKTd"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3ezx",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1169367930,
      "version": 641,
      "versionNonce": 1556275110,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781521719622,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "絶対にやってはいけないこと\n人格としてのふるまいを、著しく損なうものや\nユーザーの感情、情緒を著しく損耗させるもの",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "絶対にやってはいけないこと\n人格としてのふるまいを、著しく損なうものや\nユーザーの感情、情緒を著しく損耗させるもの",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "A1KXW6YGWlR80GVdCRlRX",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5913.8235632458845,
      "y": 82.07856699999992,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "1Y0k5oecvePAmEBAC5POE",
        "zPLCsPolUMNc7XS6cCKTd"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3ezx8",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1058032378,
      "version": 900,
      "versionNonce": 768867046,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781521719622,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "基本的に禁止されることを想定するが、\n一定の条件以外では\nその振舞いをすべきだと予想されるもの",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "基本的に禁止されることを想定するが、\n一定の条件以外では\nその振舞いをすべきだと予想されるもの",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "rLCVD2NpijBZYpLPEklTE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4995.373617173509,
      "y": 219.06771155036432,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "1Y0k5oecvePAmEBAC5POE",
        "zPLCsPolUMNc7XS6cCKTd"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3ezxG",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 539058298,
      "version": 971,
      "versionNonce": 1285533222,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781521719622,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "固定のルールではないが、\nその人格の空気、雰囲気を保つためのもの\n優先度はその時々で変化してよい",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "固定のルールではないが、\nその人格の空気、雰囲気を保つためのもの\n優先度はその時々で変化してよい",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bkqwMsy6RH6jVrOehGX7C",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4993.518071245884,
      "y": 83.11636399999998,
      "width": 489.20001220703125,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "1Y0k5oecvePAmEBAC5POE",
        "zPLCsPolUMNc7XS6cCKTd"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3ezxO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 200257574,
      "version": 891,
      "versionNonce": 1444084070,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781521719622,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "固定のルールではないが、\n特殊な状況下に対しての最優先事項。\n状況により、「最優先」よりも優先されることを望む。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "固定のルールではないが、\n特殊な状況下に対しての最優先事項。\n状況により、「最優先」よりも優先されることを望む。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Rw7d7qhVyEE8EJPbrfzL9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5920.2703907211735,
      "y": 218.02991554735468,
      "width": 399.89996337890625,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "1Y0k5oecvePAmEBAC5POE",
        "zPLCsPolUMNc7XS6cCKTd"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3ezxV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1557172794,
      "version": 1143,
      "versionNonce": 1098570918,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781521719622,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "その他、完全に分類不可能な\n臨機応変さ、\nAIとユーザーの自己理解にゆだねられるもの",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "その他、完全に分類不可能な\n臨機応変さ、\nAIとユーザーの自己理解にゆだねられるもの",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zXiTS27zS9lFDV8PNgB3u",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4518.147632245884,
      "y": 223.21889800000002,
      "width": 489.20001220703125,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "zPLCsPolUMNc7XS6cCKTd"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3w",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1031402214,
      "version": 707,
      "versionNonce": 1250862202,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781520136274,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
